{"tid":265254,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[聲優] 最鍾意邊對螢幕情侶?","createTime":"2017-05-31T13:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T05:57:09.000Z","uid":8369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb20f03eb1850f42416a37943a5b10a61f751c8","tid":265254,"uid":8369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"近年迷上睇人放閃 好似上左癮咁要成日搵藥食<br />\n叫較近期既松岡愛衣呢對當然不得不提 我都幾鍾意睇<br />\n不過自從近日發現左以下呢對之後 松岡愛衣對我既藥力就大減<br />\n如果話松岡愛衣係閃光彈 咁小山力也+柚木涼香根本係原子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柚木姐對小山既攻勢無轉彎抹角 全部直球睇得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n可能年代久遠關係相對無而家限制咁多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av4111822/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav4111822%2F&d=SKgAetXxONuB2%2Fe424Ltrf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5fcd6337\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av4111822/</a><br />\n呢段就睇到我津津樂道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然柚木姐十年前已經唔係十八廿二 但都可以嬌悄如懷春少女咁<br />\n舉手投足唔似係扮出黎 加上豪邁既性格 <br />\n搞到已經完全迷上左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奈何佢出席活動好似唔多 <br />\n連最出名既傳頌之物廣播都係得十幾集有字幕<br />\n無晒藥食好煎熬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知連登會唔會有柚木姐既同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家都分享下鍾意邊對螢幕情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdda44670f1e896bf08c0139de08bb4f2a4f158","tid":265254,"uid":35608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"百合得唔得"},{"pid":"4fba241ed5269caa3cc2ec8beba781ca5fd861e8","tid":265254,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"問題黎啦 究竟松岡愛衣係咪情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211b07af0d59480c858e1948979c3fd4c35d8e87","tid":265254,"uid":8369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百合得唔得</blockquote><br />\n當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>問題黎啦 究竟松岡愛衣係咪情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要真實情侶可以唔洗討論 無咩邊對<br />\n剩係諗到鈴村真綾"},{"pid":"5ae656356c4d03a32150836f5e0e3bfeb177a32e","tid":265254,"uid":5123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T21:56:26.000Z","msg":"松岡愛衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCharlotte嗰期內山昂輝同佐倉綾音又係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64027d43b723394ecdeaf1d1debe9b3131585dd","tid":265254,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:47:11.000Z","msg":"澤城美雪 宮野真守<br />\n佢地成日扮夫妻互動笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d06f8b25ba709e80eac30317b4870bf1358abf","tid":265254,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:02:13.000Z","msg":"二人白皇 通關感想<br />\n柚木第一句就係久遠係同邊個生"},{"pid":"9530551f32b0b7dfae193dea90cf34ca81271a96","tid":265254,"uid":8369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二人白皇 通關感想<br />\n柚木第一句就係久遠係同邊個生</blockquote><br />\n邊境女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經幻想到小山口疾疾個樣"},{"pid":"4f17944a5c99140568118cea02935db88436cd0a","tid":265254,"uid":8369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>松岡愛衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCharlotte嗰期內山昂輝同佐倉綾音又係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有男恐既佐倉竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>澤城美雪 宮野真守